name: Generative Painting 29062020 001
description: A series of generative 3D paintings mixing analogue and digital media. The process began by using actual paint and brushes and converted the scans into normal maps for the 3D shapes.  In Cinema 4D I designed a series of procedural components randomly generating new combinations and obj. By changing the seed number, the compositions are always unique and unexpected.  Part of ongoing research of interaction between me and the machine exploring new ways to influence each other looking for beauty in
